Hyper-Developer version 0.03

This module provides the Developer Tools for Hyper
the Web 3.0 Pioneering Framework.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


